Hook.

4
00:00:07,240 --> 00:00:09,599
$0100 to $030.

5
00:00:09,599 --> 00:00:13,759
I was drowning in 847 open browser tabs.

6
00:00:13,759 --> 00:00:16,280
12 half finished notes apps.

7
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:21,000
And a notion workspace so bloated it took eight seconds to load.

8
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,080
Then I build a second brain using Obsidian and Free AI plugins.

9
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:27,400
Total cost.

10
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:28,960
$0.

11
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:29,960
Result.

12
00:00:29,960 --> 00:00:31,760
I remember everything.

13
00:00:31,760 --> 00:00:33,679
Write 3x faster.

14
00:00:33,679 --> 00:00:36,120
