15
00:00:36,120 --> 00:00:41,640
And I am going to show you exactly how to build yours in the next ten minutes.

16
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:42,640
Content.

17
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:43,640
Section 1.

18
00:00:43,640 --> 00:00:47,240
What is a second brain and why most people build it wrong?

19
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:51,079
A second brain is not a fancy note-taking system.

20
00:00:51,079 --> 00:00:54,880
It is an externalized memory that thinks like you do.

21
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:59,719
Most people fail because they try to organize notes into folders before they understand

22
00:00:59,719 --> 00:01:01,400
their own.

23
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:02,800
Thinking patterns.

24
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:05,879
Chiago Forte's paramethid works.

25
00:01:05,879 --> 00:01:07,600
But only if you adapt it.

26
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:10,320
I use a modified version.

27
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:11,320
Projects.

28
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,320
Knowledge.

29
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:13,719
AI generated.

30
00:01:13,719 --> 00:01:14,840
And archive.

31
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:17,920
It lives entirely inside Obsidian.

32
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:20,120
Sync for free via GitHub.

33
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:24,320
And augmented by two AI plugins that cost nothing.

34
00:01:24,319 --> 00:01:25,319
Section 2.

35
00:01:25,319 --> 00:01:26,759
Obsidian setup.

36
00:01:26,759 --> 00:01:28,959
The free foundation.

37
00:01:28,959 --> 00:01:32,319
Obsidian is free for personal use and runs locally.

38
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:33,879
No subscription.

39
00:01:33,879 --> 00:01:35,759
No cloud dependency.

40
00:01:35,759 --> 00:01:37,399
No vendor lock in.

41
00:01:37,399 --> 00:01:41,159
First, install these community plugins.

42
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:44,560
Data view for dynamic note dashboards.

43
00:01:44,560 --> 00:01:47,479
Templator for automatic metadata injection.

44
00:01:47,479 --> 00:01:51,479
And Obsidian Git for free version backup to GitHub.

45
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:54,000
Your vault structure should be flat.

46
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:56,040
One folder per project.

47
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:58,079
One folder for sources.

48
00:01:58,079 --> 00:02:01,560
And everything else link via tags and backlinks.

49
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:04,040
The magic is not the folders.

50
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:07,200
It is the connections between ideas.

51
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,199
Section 3.

52
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:12,240
The AI plugins that turn notes into intelligence.

53
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:14,719
Here is where it gets unfair.

54
00:02:14,719 --> 00:02:17,159
Install the smart connections plugin.

55
00:02:17,159 --> 00:02:21,159
It embeds every note into a vector space locally.

56
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:23,400
Zero API calls.

57
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,599
Pro cost.

58
00:02:24,599 --> 00:02:28,159
And surfaces related ideas you forgot you wrote.

59
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:33,520
Then add local images plus to have AI describe your screenshots and diagrams automatically

60
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:35,280
using.

61
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:36,840
Local vision models.

62
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,840
The result?

63
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:43,000
You type client-pitch stress points and your second brain surfaces every related meeting

64
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,360
note.

65
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,520
Book highlight.

66
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:48,400
And random thought from the past two years.

67
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:53,360
It feels like having a research assistant who has read your entire mind.

68
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,360
Section 4.

69
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,440
The daily workflow.

70
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,200
Takes 7 minutes.

71
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,200
Morning.

72
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:04,080
I dump every thought into a daily note using voice to text on my phone.

73
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,080
Midday.

74
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:10,680
I run smart connections to see which past notes relate to today's problems evening.

75
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:16,840
I tag three notes for AI summarization and move finished project notes to archive.

76
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:19,560
The entire system runs offline.

77
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:21,760
No cloud AI required.

78
00:03:21,759 --> 00:03:23,479
No subscription.

79
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:27,199
Just a free app and a discipline 7 minute habit.

80
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:28,399
