81
00:03:28,399 --> 00:03:31,079
Real results after 90 days.

82
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:36,120
Before this system, I rewrote the same introductions three times because I forgot where

83
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,599
I saved the first draft.

84
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:43,319
Now I have a searchable library of 2,400 ideas.

85
00:03:43,319 --> 00:03:45,719
87 book summaries.

86
00:03:45,719 --> 00:03:49,079
And 145 client call insights.

87
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:52,680
My article output went from 2 per month to 6.

88
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:56,040
My anxiety about forgetting things disappeared.

89
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:58,320
The system is not sexy.

90
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,800
It is invisible.

91
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,120
That is the point.

92
